# CYD - ZX Spectrum Emulator

This is a ZX Spectrum emulator for ESP32 boards configured for the CYD, with a touch-screen keyboard:

- [firmware/](mdc:firmware/) - Contains the main ESP32 firmware code
  - [firmware/src/main.cpp](mdc:firmware/src/main.cpp) - Main entry point for the firmware
  - [firmware/platformio.ini](mdc:firmware/platformio.ini) - PlatformIO configuration for supported boards
  
- [keyboard-server/](mdc:keyboard-server/) - Python code for using a desktop keyboard as input
- [docs/](mdc:docs/) - Documentation and images
- [desktop/](mdc:desktop/) - Desktop emulation applications

## Supported Hardware
- Cheap Yellow Display (CYD)
